Common stat functions

  • Mode is not present
  • But easy to create
getmode <- function(v) {
  uniqv <- unique(v)
  uniqv[which.max(tabulate(match(v, uniqv)))]
}
apply(cars, 2, getmode)
## speed  dist 
##    20    26
